test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:18:103  |    PRINT: "信步走來，行了"
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:18:103  |    PRINT: 「去路」
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:18:103  |    PRINT: "里路，遇見幾戶人家？想來是"
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:18:103  |    PRINT: 「人家」
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:18:103  |    PRINT: "戶矣。"
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:20:40   |    PRINT: "亭臺六七座，八九十枝花。"
