test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:36:37   |    PRINT: "老夫掐指一總，路、村、亭、花，此行共覽風物"
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:36:37   |    PRINT: 「萬物」
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:36:37   |    PRINT: "件。"
test/questions_en/05_village_arithmetic.wy:36:37   |    PRINT: "想當然耳，風雅竟能稱斤論兩，妙極妙極！"
